div.div:
1. Naming
1. Rules
1. case sensitive
2. no length limit, sequence of Unicode letters and digits
3. begin with a letter (convention) or "_" or "$", but "_" and "$" not encouraged
4. subsequent characters may be letters, digits, dollar signs or underscore characters
2. Styles
1. use camelCase
2. class name captitalizes the initial letter
3. constant value capitalizes every letter and separates subsequent words with underscore
4. method names should be a verb in lowercase or a multi-word name beginning with a verb in lowercase followed by adjectives, nouns, etc.
